chain.description: I see that the user wants to assess the drug responses of the attendees for a charity event. They specifically mentioned gathering information on the current COVID-19 cases in the event location. To fulfill their request, I will call the 'drug_responses_for_23andme' function with the argument 'profile_id' set to 'attendee1'. This will allow me to retrieve the drug response data for the attendee's profile. Additionally, I will need to call the 'covid_19_by_api_ninjas' function to gather information on the current COVID-19 cases in the event location. By doing so, I can provide the user with the necessary data for their charity event.
